				<td colspan="2"><span>Yeah, since you know they're going there, it couldn't hurt to ask them if they would mind if you went along. As long as you do your share, they probably won't mind.
<br />

<br />
It's hard to say what your chances are of getting the whip. I went up there once and cleared out all the amy's and no whip. I went up there a second time and it dropped on my 2nd kill. The first time I went up there I knew that a guild had cleared it about 8 hours prior, including the golems, so I knew it would be safe. The second time a guild was up there. I asked them if they minded if I hunted amy's and they said no.
<br />

<br />
The respawn is something like 4-6 hours on trash and 3 days I believe for the DT golems.</span></td>
