<br />
I have to give a big thanks to Guild Dawnfire on Inny!
<br />

<br />
I joined their raid on Saturday.  Two guildies were in front of me.  We started on West Wall and moved counter-clockwise.  A Whip dropped early, then as we moved away from CT, no more Amy Warriors.
<br />

<br />
Once we were at high noon,  we started pulling the Warriors again.  Another Whip dropped.  Pulled more Warriors and . . . . on the <i>very last</i> Amygdalan Warrior, I got my drop!
<br />

<br />
Now if people would just stop farming Trak for Kunark BP's . . . .
<br />

<br />
Thanks again Dawnfire!
